enum vqec_show_tuner_options_mask

The enum values defined in vqec_show_tuner_options_mask and used by vqec_set_options_flag() return info derived from the parsing of a "show tuner..." CLI command, including:

1. the keyword that followed "show tuner", which is one of: a.) "all" (ALL_TUNERS_MASK) b.) "name" (SPECIFIC_TUNER_MASK) c.) "join-delay" (JOINDELAY_MASK) 2. in the case of a "all" or "name" keyword, the set of flags given to qualify the "show tuner" output. The ALL_OPTIONS_MASK defines the complete set of flags for this purpose. 3. whether an error was encountered in parsing the keywords, flags, or tuner names (ERROR_MASK or TUNER_NAME_ERROR_MASK)
